.vercel

# Never commit build artifacts or databases to this repo.
# This folder is the deploy source for a PUBLIC website: anything committed here
# can end up downloadable by anyone. An installer built before 2026-07-10 embeds
# a real merchant's database (the seed.db incident) — those binaries must never
# enter git history, where removing them costs a filter-repo + force-push.
*.exe
*.apk
*.msi
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
